Set the default HTTP Status to use for redirects._

By default this is {@link HttpStatus#SEE_OTHER}._@param status the 3xx redirect status to use
codeText: public void setRedirectStatus(HttpStatus status) {_		Assert.notNull(status, "HttpStatus is required")__		Assert.isTrue(status.is3xxRedirection(), "Not a redirect status: " + status)__		this.redirectStatus = status__	}
